title: James Webb and NASA’s Early Days
itunes:title: James Webb and NASA’s Early Days
description:
People are often surprised to learn that the namesake for the James Webb Space Telescope wasn't a scientist or engineer, but a lawyer and a bureaucrat. He was NASA's second administrator, and led the agency through incredibly difficult times.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
